dct_title_s: UMedia: John R. Borchert Map Library
dct_description_sm: UMedia provides open access to digitized materials from across the University of Minnesota.

The John R. Borchert Map Library contains an extensive collection of historic maps and atlases. Though the focus is on historic Minnesota items, the collection contains a wide range of topics and dates -- from historic items dating back to the 16th Century to current maps from around the world.
